<h2>Methodology</h2>
<p>I believe that the best design is made through diverse research, close collaboration, and constant experimentation, iteration, and feedback.</p>
<p>My practice is deeply rooted in systems design, which includes but is certainly not limited to design and interaction systems, product strategy, and user experience design.</p>
<ol class="process-list">
<img src="/assets/images/profile/research.svg" alt="Research Icon">
<li><strong>Research</strong> — The fun part. I "go deep" on the subject matter to gain conceptual understanding of its ground truths. Additionally, I do a good deal of competitive research to establish prior art that can be learned from. From there, I like to say that the design process becomes one of "lateral discovery" in which I seek to find alternative solutions within the constraints of a problem statement.</li>
<img src="/assets/images/profile/strategy.svg" alt="Strategy">
<li><strong>Strategy</strong> — I work collaboratively with stakeholders to create design and project strategies based on my research and the requirements of a project. The goal of strategy is, among other things, to create a shared language and vision that can be used to measure the success of the work.</li>
<img src="/assets/images/profile/design.svg" alt="Design">
<li><strong>Design &amp; Iterate</strong> — I explore as many ideas as possible, as rapidly as possible, to begin reaching solutions that address the defined problem statement. This process is iterative, collaborative, and ideally done in the open rather than behind closed doors.</li>
<img src="/assets/images/profile/delivery.svg" alt="Delivery">
<li><strong>Delivery</strong> — The final deliverables (be they instructions, screens, files, code, principles, poems, playlists, typefaces, questions, or something else) are delivered comprehensively and with detailed documentation of process and implementation. Strong documentation ensures the posterity of ideas established during the design process, making maintainence of the delivered items much easier.</li>
<img src="/assets/images/profile/afterwards.svg" alt="Afterwards">
<li><strong>Afterward</strong> — I maintain long-term relationships with stakeholders to ensure the long-term success of solutions produced by this process.</li>
</ol>


